Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:08.72,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:727894,728728}{NOTE:—おう！\\N—おう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:33.21,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:751459,753211}{NOTE:凄い。さすがに迫力あるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.09,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:755213,757090}{NOTE:さ、もういいでしょ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:38.29,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:757090,758299}{NOTE:社長はお待ちからですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:48.55,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:766473,768559}{NOTE:くそ。車の調子が可笑しいぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:56.27,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:775233,776276}{NOTE:ちくしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:58.52,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:776276,778528}{NOTE:もう少しで丸日紡績だって言うのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:12:59.44,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:778528,779445}{NOTE:どうです？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:01.28,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:779445,781281}{NOTE:気に入りましたか？我がバレー部。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:02.49,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:781281,782490}{NOTE:え。凄いわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:04.36,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:782490,784367}{NOTE:やっぱり実業は違うわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:09.49,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:784367,789497}{NOTE:いいえ、いいえ。鮎原さんが直ぐ我が社のエースに。社長もきっとお喜びになるでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:11.91,Sign,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789497,791915}{NOTE:社長室}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:15.50,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:794377,795503}{NOTE:入りたまえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:16.87,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:795503,796879}{NOTE:さ、鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:21.63,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:800925,801634}{NOTE:お。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:24.92,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:802051,804929}{NOTE:あ、社長。鮎原こずえさんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:26.59,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:804929,806597}{NOTE:よろしくお願いします。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:29.60,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:807056,809600}{NOTE:え、さ、さ。どうぞ。そこにかけなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:809600,810810}{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:38.81,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:816065,818818}{NOTE:君のことは私もよく知っている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:42.48,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:818818,822488}{NOTE:なんとしても家の車で実力を発揮してもらいたい。頼みますよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:44.94,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:823031,824949}{NOTE:はい。有難うございます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:47.78,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:825658,827785}{NOTE:バレー一筋に打ち込んでください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:50.91,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:827785,830913}{NOTE:仕事の方は適当に融通つけるからね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:53.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:830913,833708}{NOTE:あら、だって。そんなの嫌だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:54.75,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:833708,834751}{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:57.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:834751,837712}{NOTE:バレーをやるからって特別扱いされるのは嫌です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:00.29,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:837712,840298}{NOTE:学校でもちゃんと普通に試験を受けてきました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:01.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:840298,841424}{NOTE:練習は練習。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:02.59,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:841424,842592}{NOTE:勉強は勉強。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:05.17,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:842592,845178}{NOTE:ん、それはそうだが、んん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:07.97,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:845178,847972}{NOTE:私バレーでお給料もらうじゃありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:10.35,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:847972,850350}{NOTE:仕事は仕事。バリバリやります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:11.80,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:850350,851809}{NOTE:ん、よろしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:15.10,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:851809,855104}{NOTE:君のアマチュアスポーツ推進が気に入ったぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:16.31,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:855104,856314}{NOTE:どうも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:19.40,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:856314,859400}{NOTE:が君大手柄だ。対したお嬢さんを用途としたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.81,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:859400,860818}{NOTE:は、恐れ入ります、社長。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:23.78,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:861486,863780}{NOTE:私生意気のこと言ったかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:26.40,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:864864,866407}{NOTE:いいえ、いいえ、とんでもない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:29.53,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:867033,869535}{NOTE:そうですか？じゃ、よかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.28,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:869535,871287}{NOTE:社長さんって話せるんですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:32.53,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:871287,872538}{NOTE:いや。はは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:34.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:872538,874082}{NOTE:顔に見合わず。あ—}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:35.20,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:874665,875208}{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:37.00,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:875208,877001}{NOTE:あははは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:41.46,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:878211,881464}{NOTE:だが、鮎原くん、君は確か未だ未成年だったろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:43.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:882090,883424}{NOTE:え。そうですが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:48.51,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:884842,888513}{NOTE:ん、それなら契約にはご両親のOKが必要だね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:51.68,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:890223,891682}{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.35,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:891682,893351}{NOTE:や、何。心配いらん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:57.43,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:893351,897438}{NOTE:え、ご両親には私からよくお話してみる。きっと賛成してくださるでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:14:58.85,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:898147,898856}{NOTE:そうですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:17.04,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:916249,917041}{NOTE:こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:20.04,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:917333,920044}{NOTE:それではお父さんにはよく頼んで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:21.79,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:921003,921796}{NOTE:こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:22.50,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:921796,922505}{NOTE:あ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:33.30,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:930221,933307}{NOTE:これは、これは。あなたは鮎原くんのお父さんでしたか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:36.01,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:934392,936017}{NOTE:あ、は、はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:37.22,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:936017,937228}{NOTE:あ、丁度よかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:42.23,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:937228,942233}{NOTE:お嬢さんの契約に関してはお父様にお話しておかなければならんこともありましたので。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:43.69,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:942233,943693}{NOTE:さ、さ。どうぞ。こちらへ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:54.62,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:952827,954620}{NOTE:心配ないさ。大丈夫。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:57.62,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:954620,957623}{NOTE:きっと社長は上手く君のパパを丸めてくれるよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:58.58,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:957623,958583}{NOTE:あ、どこ行くんです？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:15:59.91,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:958583,959917}{NOTE:バレーの練習を見てきます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:06.46,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:964338,966466}{NOTE:え、一つ今日は私が如何に…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:08.75,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:966466,968759}{NOTE:しかし社長さん、父親としましては…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:10.30,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:968759,970303}{NOTE:ま、いいじゃないですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:14.64,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:970303,974640}{NOTE:バレーファンであり鮎原さんファンであるからについてじっくりお話しいたしますかな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:27.48,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:986194,987487}{NOTE:なぜかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:31.36,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:987487,991365}{NOTE:私は今パパが社長さんに絶対に進学させます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:33.15,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:991365,993159}{NOTE:そう言って欲しいと思っている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:35.32,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:993159,995328}{NOTE:私のしたことは間違ってるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.41,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:995328,997413}{NOTE:そうだったな、鮎原こずえ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:40.12,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:999207,1000124}{NOTE:すみません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:41.29,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000124,1001292}{NOTE:ボールとってください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:42.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002043,1002752}{NOTE:は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:44.67,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003169,1004670}{NOTE:ボールを投げて！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.96,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006255,1007964}{NOTE:いいえ。間違ってやしない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:54.30,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012845,1014305}{NOTE:あ。凄いサーブ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:57.68,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015223,1017683}{NOTE:その変まで来て、垂直の落ちたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:01.14,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018059,1021145}{NOTE:通りてどこかで見た顔だと思ったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.60,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021521,1023606}{NOTE:あや、キャプテンあの人知ってるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:05.65,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024440,1025650}{NOTE:鮎原こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:07.77,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025650,1027777}{NOTE:ジュニアバレーの日本代表よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:10.07,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027777,1030071}{NOTE:じゃ、富士見中学バレー部のキャプテンね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:11.48,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030655,1031489}{NOTE:ま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:13.61,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031489,1033616}{NOTE:今のサーブは「木の葉落とし」だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:15.03,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033616,1035034}{NOTE:進学するって聞いてたけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:17.91,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036244,1037912}{NOTE:内に入ることになったのかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:19.45,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038412,1039455}{NOTE:呼んでみましょうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:20.62,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039455,1040623}{NOTE:鮎原さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:21.33,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040623,1041332}{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:23.87,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041332,1043876}{NOTE:あなた富士見中の鮎原こずえでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.00,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043876,1045002}{NOTE:はい。よろしく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:27.37,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046169,1047379}{NOTE:やっぱり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:28.83,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047379,1048839}{NOTE:私達の仲間に成るのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:30.29,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049715,1050299}{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:34.38,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051342,1054387}{NOTE:お嬢さんの決心は1時の浮ついた気持ちじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:39.64,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054387,1059642}{NOTE:バレーボール界の名門我が丸日紡績で力いっぱい自分の実力を試してみたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:41.01,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059642,1061018}{NOTE:そして仕事もしたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:42.47,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061018,1062478}{NOTE:純粋な気持ちです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:44.81,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062478,1064814}{NOTE:お父さん。どうでしょう？ここは一つ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:46.02,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065189,1066023}{NOTE:は～。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:50.40,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066023,1070403}{NOTE:しかし娘の本当の考えがどこにあるのか？一体。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:51.90,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070403,1071904}{NOTE:それならはっきりしてるでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:54.24,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071904,1074240}{NOTE:悪が丸日で思う存分戦いたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:55.90,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074240,1075908}{NOTE:こういうことではないのですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:56.74,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075908,1076742}{NOTE:は～。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:06.37,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085001,1086377}{NOTE:素晴らしいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:06.37,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085626,1086377}{NOTE:かっこいい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:07.33,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086377,1087336}{NOTE:こずえくん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:08.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087336,1088754}{NOTE:努くん。どうして？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:12.46,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090923,1092466}{NOTE:何なの彼？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:14.01,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092466,1094010}{NOTE:彼女のボーイフレンド、きっと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:17.34,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094927,1097346}{NOTE:君はあそこで何をしていた？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:18.51,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097346,1098514}{NOTE:この会社は君の何なんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:20.43,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099223,1100433}{NOTE:何いって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:23.14,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100433,1103144}{NOTE:学校卒業したら私ここへ就職するの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:23.93,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103144,1103936}{NOTE:馬鹿！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:24.43,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103936,1104437}{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:25.60,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104437,1105605}{NOTE:酷いわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:28.39,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105605,1108399}{NOTE:暴力不良何て…止めしてましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:29.56,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108399,1109567}{NOTE:お止しなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:30.81,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109567,1110818}{NOTE:練習中よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:32.57,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110818,1112570}{NOTE:練習中はバレーのことだけ考えて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:35.32,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113154,1115322}{NOTE:人はいるから。向こうで話そう。さ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:41.16,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119744,1121162}{NOTE:ん、何よするの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:45.24,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121162,1125249}{NOTE:いきなり突き飛ばしたり張ってきたり、いくら努くんだって許せないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:49.42,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126207,1129420}{NOTE:こうでもしなきゃ。君の目が覚めないと思ったからだ。}
