Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:22.95,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160784,1162953}{NOTE:すまない、こずえくん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:25.37,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162953,1165373}{NOTE:しかし、そんな同情はごめんだ。}
