Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:36.21,Default,Director,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175257,1176217}{NOTE:んん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:40.72,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176967,1180721}{NOTE:君を犠牲にして僕だけしといてノコノコ進学できるもんか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:42.84,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181847,1182848}{NOTE:犠牲？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:44.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182848,1184392}{NOTE:大げさなこと言わないで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:46.60,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184392,1186602}{NOTE:ここへ入ったってバレーがちゃんとできるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:47.77,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186602,1187770}{NOTE:じゃ、学校はどうする？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:49.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188229,1189814}{NOTE:そ、そんなどうだっていいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:50.85,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189814,1190856}{NOTE:何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:52.02,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190856,1192024}{NOTE:いい加減にしろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:52.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192024,1192524}{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.11,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193359,1195110}{NOTE:未だ戻ってこないわ、あの二人。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:56.73,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195110,1196737}{NOTE:あいつ不良だったんじゃない?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:19:57.61,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196737,1197613}{NOTE:ちょっと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:59.36,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197613,1199365}{NOTE:いつまで気にしてるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:00.49,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199365,1200491}{NOTE:すみません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.86,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200491,1202868}{NOTE:けど、気になるのは当たり前です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:05.28,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202868,1205287}{NOTE:あの子は来てくれたら凄い戦力になるわ。}
